Setup steps on EmailJs website 
To integrate emailjs with our website > https://www.emailjs.com/

Step 1: Create an account on EmailJS website > Create Free Account > SignUp

Step 2: Create Email Service  
         Email Service > Add New Service > Google select > Continue > send email on your behalf checkbox-checked >  continue > create service

Step 3: Create Email Template
        Like This : 	
            Hello {{name}},

            You got a new message from {{from_name}}:

            {{from_email}}

            {{from_message}}

            Portfolio Site
Save the template with click on save..
